(1, '2022-04-10', 1, 'template-whyWithUs', 'single', 'Why with us?', 'Because we are the best', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Amongst the crowd of new adventure companies sprouting every day, we are committed to responsible and sustainable tourism and have something of a history, culture, and experience that stands out for the technical infallibility, excellent management, and sincerity in providing services.</p>', NULL, 'why-with-us', '1612785656727551693', 1, 0, 0, 1, 'why-with-us-55VY2cmjm1UWYRANZgcQivhB0cir1291gPUVT7Oj.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'Seven Summit Treks;', 'Seven Summit Treks;', '<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p></p><p>Amongst the crowd of new adventure companies sprouting\r\nevery day, we are committed to responsible and sustainable tourism and have\r\nsomething of a history, culture, and experience that stands out for the\r\ntechnical infallibility, excellent management, and sincerity in providing\r\nservices.</p><p></p><p></p>', NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2021-02-08 12:00:56', '2022-06-26 09:32:39'),
(2, '2022-04-13', 1, 'template-whoWeAre', 'single', 'Who we are?', 'Leading Expedition Operator', '<p>From its establishment and humble beginning in 2009, our directors led SST through the years as the biggest, safest, and most responsible mountain adventure operator in Nepal. In 2011, SST took the responsibility of organizing and managing the Government of Nepal&rsquo;s first Civil Servants&rsquo; Mt. Everest Expedition which was a huge success and a national pride. This expedition bolstered the theme of SST as a professional and reliable expedition operator. Over the years, SST has been labeled as Nepal&rsquo;s biggest taxpayer in the Trekking and Mountaineering sector and has been awarded by the Ministry of Culture, Tourism and Civil Aviation in 2023.</p>\r\n<p>Our Founding Director, Mr. Mingma Sherpa started his mountaineering journey in 1996 as a porter. His fascination for heights led him to bigger mountains and this journey eventually got him to become the first South-Asian climber to finish all 14 8000 meter mountains. Chhang Dawa Sherpa, our Director has also completed all 14 8000ers and leads SST&rsquo;s big mountain climbs. Mr. Mingma Sherpa &amp; his brother Mr. Chhang Dawa Sherpa held the record of \"World\'s First Two Brothers\" to have completed the 14 8000ers. This is a single record in the world\'s mountaineering history. Tashi Lakpa Sherpa and Pasang Phurba Sherpa are equally competent are dedicated climbers as well as climbing administrators. This valiant image of our directors and their unparalleled dedication to operating safe adventures has led SST to be Nepal&rsquo;s biggest.</p>\r\n<p>Statistically, there are thousands of treks and expedition operators in Nepal. However, some specific qualities distinguish us from the rest. We excel at:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Top-notch gears and equipment that is upgraded in compliance with market availability</li>\r\n<li>Competent and professional field staff</li>\r\n<li>Strategic positioning of logistics in Nepal&rsquo;s key adventure areas to meet clients\' requirements with ease</li>\r\n<li>High success rate with near zero fatality in big mountains</li>\r\n<li>Customizable and tailored services as the client deems</li>\r\n<li>Prompt Helicopter rescue services as needed</li>\r\n<li>International Organizer &ndash; Successful Adventures in Himalaya, Karakoram, Andes, Alps, Rockies, African mountains and anywhere the client wishes</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seven Summit Treks, is a Nepalese adventure operator, specializing in 8000ers and offers the major logistics in the Himalayas. Established by four mountaineer brothers, we have a network of experienced professionals spread across Nepal, China, and Pakistan, who will strive to make your mountaineering and trekking experience worthwhile.</p>', 'who-we-are', '1612785791728427371', 1, 0, 0, 2, '2000x1200-banner-who-we-are-h7p3rsz8zJrzH6MdkeJ7eNZds7swBHUMBcfbEJ1r.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Seven Summit Treks is a registered Nepali trek and expedition operator specializing in the Himalayan climbs and niche/ personalized adventures.&nbsp; Established in 2009 by four Sherpa brothers who share a profound love for mountains and mountaineering SST has grown over the years to become Nepal&rsquo;s one of the biggest adventure operators with global networks that allow us and our guests to achieve any adventure dream around the world.</p>', NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 'en', '2021-02-08 12:03:11', '2024-02-29 10:01:26'),
(3, '2022-02-10', 1, 'template-history', 'single', 'Our History', 'Our History', '<p>Amongst the crowd of new expedition and trekking companies sprouting every day, Seven Summit Treks has something of a history, culture and experience that stands out for the technical infallibility, excellent management and sincerity in providing services.</p>', 'Amongst the crowd of new expedition and trekking companies sprouting every day, Seven Summit Treks has something of a history, culture and experience that stands out for the technical infallibility, excellent management and sincerity in providing services.', 'our-history', '1612785982569086021', 1, 0, 0, 3, 'wp2752142-Wv25XKZKjIZCTm7UNHnVO43h9qW4WUowbFbPmryc.jpg', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2021-02-08 12:06:22', '2024-03-08 06:18:56'),
(4, '2022-04-13', 1, 'template-chairmanMessage', 'single', 'Chairman\'s Message', 'Mingma Sherpa', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seven Summit Treks has employed hundreds of Sherpa people, who belong to an underprivileged minority caste in Nepal. This has brought about significant change in their quality of life. We feel a great sense of accomplishment for facilitating many young mountaineers to conquer mountains. We also feel proud in stating that many of the clients whose expedition was conducted by us were able to climb mountains above 8000 meters on their first attempt.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Today, Seven Summit Treks has developed a formidable reputation and has been gaining a lot of competition from international trekking and expedition firms. It is all but natural that we are being dragged in the mud while being guilty of nothing. But this has led to some negative publicity for the company and some raised eyebrows. However, we don&rsquo;t want to go on pointing fingers at certain parties who have tried to muddle the reputation of our company. Understandably, some parties aren&rsquo;t really happy as we continue ascending toward the pinnacle of success. We sincerely request you not to pay heed to any of such rumors and evaluate us only after gaining firsthand experience of our services. No matter what people blame us for, we are prepared and committed, as ever to fulfilling the needs of our widespread clientele. Both of us directors of Seven Summit Treks have had years of experience in mountaineering as we both have conquered all the 14 highest peaks in the world. This organization is run by experienced mountaineers ever since the time of inception and is valid proof of the technical excellence of our organization. Presently, we not just possess the ability to provide our clients with what they desire but also to facilitate competing firms and agencies during dire times. We are frequently known to assist other treks and expedition agencies during times of distress, like providing helicopters for several rescue missions. We declare that we will continue to remain the number one organizer of expeditions and trekking in Nepal.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mingma Sherpa</strong><br />Chairman<br />Seven Summit Treks</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Amongst the crowd of new adventure companies sprouting every day, Seven Summit Treks has something of a history, culture, and experience that comes with it. With years of experience in catering to the needs of our clients spread throughout the world, we now have thousands of satisfied customers who strongly recommend Seven Summit Treks. We have been standing out for our technical infallibility, excellent management, and sincerity in providing services. Be it a trek across the vast stretches of rolling hills or the expedition to the summit of majestic peaks, we are here to help you reclaim freedom and wilderness. Established back in 2010 AD, we have already aided a generation of nature enthusiasts to discover the bewildering beauty and the incomparable splendor of the Himalayas. And if you have cravings to get in touch with nature, dive deep inside its beauty, and get back, rejuvenated, Seven Summit Treks welcomes you to Nepal.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We offer a wide range of services, and although we are based in Nepal, we already have a wide network spread in China and Pakistan. We have guides, Sherpas, and leaders who have years of experience tussling with nature and then befriending it. Our purpose is to facilitate the client&rsquo;s goal, whether it be mingling with nature, or conquering it. Be that in China or Pakistan, we will accompany you anywhere and still provide service with a sense of confidence and delight. We are proud to acknowledge that, our guides are people who find pleasure in the wide embrace of nature and they keep the safety of our clients, which is their number one priority.</p>', 'chairmans-message', '1612786086783894237', 1, 0, 0, 5, 'whatsapp-image-2022-03-14-at-12-EAasgqd6UDhTZ0EH5q4U7VnMwDtLI5I33hCnOAFF.jpeg', '', NULL, 'seven summit treks\' chairman', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2021-02-08 12:08:06', '2022-05-15 09:24:54'),
(5, '2022-03-14', 1, 'template-teamSingle', 'single', 'About Chairman', 'About Chairman', '<p>&nbsp;Mingma Sherpa</p>\r\n<p>Chairman</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;info@sevensummittreks.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;+977-9851111187</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mr. Mingma Sherpa, Chairman of Seven Summit Treks is the first person among Nepalese who successfully summit 14 mountains of the world which are above 8000 meter height without repeating and kept a new record in the world\'s history. He is one of the most experienced, responsible, dedicated and honest expedition leader of Nepal. He is now here to share his experience gained during his previous trips. All interested person can join with him in his one of the best and recognized agency to lead successful expedition and trekking. He assures you all to provide quality service and safe journey with experienced workers. Mr. Mingma Sherpa &amp; his brother Mr. Chhang Dawa Sherpa has kept world record of \"Worlds First Two Brothers\" successfully summit 14 Mountains of the world which are above 8000 meter height. This is a single record in the worlds mountaineering history.</p>\r\n<p>Mountains Summitted by Mingma Sherpa</p>\r\n<p>S.N.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Name of Mountain</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Total Summited</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Summitted Year(s)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />1</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Mount Everest (8848 m) -Nepal</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1 Times</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2004 (Spring)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />2</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>K-2 (8611 m) -Pakistan</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1 Times</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2004 (Summer)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />3</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Kanchanjunga (8586 m) -Nepal</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1 Times</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2011 (Spring)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><