(77, '2022-06-09', 1, 'single', 'single', 'US - Nepal Friendship Team stood on the top of Mt. Denali', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mt. Denali Summit Update!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">US - Nepal Friendship Team stood on the top of Mt. Denali and hoisted the US Nepal diplomatic relation diamond jubilee flag at 05.30 AM, 9 June 2022, Nepal Time (15:15 Alaska Time Zone - 8 June 2022).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mark Parella, leader of the team reported that all team members successfully scaled the highest mountain peak in North America, which stands at an elevation of 6190m above sea level.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The expedition team to climb Mt. Denali in Alaska consists of American and Nepali mountaineers to mark the 75 years of diplomatic relationship between Nepal and the USA. Earlier on 31 March, Public Affairs Chief at US Embassy in Nepal Garrett E. Wilkerson handed over the diamond jubilee&rsquo;s flag to the team in Kathmandu, and on 14 May the flag was raised to the top of the Mt. Everest by Pasang Phurba Sherpa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Climbers:</p>\r\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Mark Parella <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t93/1/16/1f1fa_1f1f8.png\" alt=\"🇺🇸\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> Exped. Leader</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Mingma Sherpa <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> 14 Peak Summiteer (Chairman-SST)</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Karma Tenzing <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> Exped. Leader</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Chhang Dawa Sherpa <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> 14 Peak Summiteer (Board Director-SST)</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Karma Gelje Sherpa <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Team Member</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Pasang Dawa Sherpa <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Team Member</li>\r\n<li dir=\"auto\">Jangbu Sherpa <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t62/1/16/1f1f3_1f1f5.png\" alt=\"🇳🇵\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Team Member</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This expedition is also organized for a cause and spread an important message that hits home, be it in the USA or anywhere in the world: \"Climb Against Cancer\".</p>\r\n</div>', '<p>US - Nepal Friendship Team stood on the top of Mt. Denali</p>', 'us-nepal-friendship-team-stood-on-the-top-of-mt-denali', '1654749156526095109', 5, 0, 0, 9, 'us-nepal-dYxkQJoDnPoTu627G8dwMK45gogFjgdJSFwdirsE.jpg', 'us-nepal-1tLrP46vrDK6Oa4ouxlUlM18lr3IZeQvm6g8b6eS.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2022-06-09 04:32:36', '2022-06-09 12:39:17'),
