(107, '2023-06-01', 1, 'single', 'single', 'SST Mt. Kangchenjunga Spring Expedition 2023 Summit Update', 'SST Mt. Kangchenjunga Spring Expedition 2023 Summit Update', '<p class=\"uk-scrollspy-inview uk-animation-slide-top-small\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A huge congratulation to our Kangchenjunga Expedition team members and Sherpas for the successful ascent of the world\'s 3rd-highest mountain this spring season.</p>\r\n<p class=\"uk-scrollspy-inview uk-animation-slide-top-small\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">After weeks of intense effort and perseverance, the climbers reached the summit of Kangchenjunga. The climbers\' unwavering dedication, coupled with the support of their skilled Sherpas and meticulous planning, enabled them to conquer the formidable peak.</p>\r\n<p class=\"uk-scrollspy-inview uk-animation-slide-top-small\">Summiteer List on different dates:</p>\r\n<p><strong>18 MAY 2023</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Kristin Harila (Norway)</li>\r\n<li>Tenjen Sherpa (Makalu-9, Sankhuwasabha)</li>\r\n<li>Gyalu Sherpa (Patle-3, Okhaldhunga)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>25 MAY 2023</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Luis Andreas Stitzinger (Germany)</li>\r\n<li>Waldemar Dominik Kowalewski (Poland)</li>\r\n<li>Adrian Laza (Romania)</li>\r\n<li>He Jing (China)</li>\r\n<li>Vadim, Pirmin Druelle (France)</li>\r\n<li>Vibeke Andrea Sefland (Norway)</li>\r\n<li>Graciela Flor Cuenca Blas (Peru)</li>\r\n<li>Chhepal Sherpa (Patle-2, Okhaldhunga)</li>\r\n<li>Nuri Sherpa (Goli-7, Solukhumbu)</li>\r\n<li>Pemba Sherpa (Makalu-5, Sankhuwasabha)</li>\r\n<li>Chhiring Bhote (Bhotkhola-3, Sankhuwasabha)</li>\r\n<li>Ang Tezin Sherpa (Makalu-9, Sankhuwasabha)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>1 JUN 2023</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Eric Wright Gilbertson (USA)</li>\r\n<li>Pemba Thenduk Sherpa (Makalu-9, Sankhuwasabha)</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p>SST Mt. Kangchenjunga Spring Expedition 2023 Summit Update</p>', 'sst-mt-kangchenjunga-spring-expedition-2023-summit-update', '168603840376744991', 5, 0, 0, 24