(46, 'Kami Rita Sherpa', 'kami-rita-sherpa', '1717393837899959054', 'Climbing Guide', '4', '5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '+977 01 4822960', 'info@sevensummittreks.com', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kami Rita Sherpa </strong>(born 17 January 1970, Solukhumbu, Nepal) is working with Seven Summit Treks as a Senior Climbing Guide. Since May 2018, he has held the record for most summits of Mt. Everest (8848.86m). His most recent ascent was his 28th, accomplished on 23 May 2023, breaking his own record set just days earlier on 17 May 2023.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kami Rita also holds the record for the most ascents of mountains above 8000 meters with a total of 43 summits. This includes 8 ascents of Cho Oyu, 5 ascents of Manaslu, and one ascent each of Lhotse and K2.</p>', NULL, '1', 1, '', 'kami-rita-sherpa-z5cZBzPtGiDhers0mvBTkdympNy2oSPRfzv9ExlW.jpg', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2022-08-26 04:21:37', '2024-06-03 05:50:37'),
