(81, 'Lakpa Sherpa', 'lakpa-sherpa', '1721367987829378735', 'Climbing Guide', '4', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/makalulakpa8463', 'https://www.instagram.com/makalu.lakpa/', NULL, NULL, '+977 01 4822960', 'info@sevensummittreks.com', '<p>Lakpa Sherpa, a senior climbing guide at Seven Summit Treks, has been climbing for the last 11 years. Lakpa began his climbing career as a junior expedition staff but always had a zeal for attaining higher heights. He started his big climbing journey with Mt. Manaslu (8163 m) in 2012 and since then has successfully climbed over 14 times - 8000ers, maintaining an astounding safety record of 100% with his climbing clients.</p>\r\n<p>In 2022, Lakpa shocked the climbing world by summiting Makalu (8463 m) 3 times in mere span of 16 days; all that while guiding and leading clients to their dream summit. This extraordinary accomplishment is recognized as an official Guinness World Record. To date, Lakpa has summited Makalu 6 times.</p>', '<p><strong>The man who summited Mt. Makalu (8485m) thrice in 16 days!</strong></p>', '1', 2, '', 'lakpa-sherpa-XXcwnyM0xHsk0rvCikgTjT2kwbM9Oz4wTepoAIsK.jpg', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2023-12-08 07:12:06', '2024-07-19 05:46:27'),
