(103, 345, 4, 'MEDICAL CHECKUP', 'A medical checkup in Kathmandu before the expedition to ensure that the member is fit to climb and identifies any potential health risks.', 13, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(104, 345, 4, 'MEMBER TRANSPORTATION', 'All Helicopter flights as per the Itinerary. From Kathmandu - Lukla - Namche, Namche - Dingboche, During the expedition return back to Kathmandu and after Expedition from Everest BC to Kathmandu.', 14, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(106, 345, 4, 'REST IN KATHMANDU', 'Helicopter flight from Everest base camp - Kathmandu - Everest Base camp via Namche (1 time) if required. Full Board accommodation at 5 Star hotel in Kathmandu.', 16, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(107, 345, 4, 'EXPEDITION STUFFS TRANSPORTATION', 'All necessary expedition equipment transportation for all Members and Staff from Kathmandu to Lukla (by air cargo) and Base camp (by Porters / Yak) – While returning: Base camp to Lukla (by porters / Yak) and Lukla to Kathmandu (by air cargo). Based on the condition, different transportation variants may adopt.', 17, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(108, 345, 4, 'TREKKING LOGISTIC', 'All necessary logistic management during the trek along with a UIAGM guide and private cook, who will cook food for a member.  Overnight stay at upgraded lodges (attached restroom) and member’s all personal belongings will be carried by porters or helicopter.', 18, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(109, 345, 4, 'PHOTOGRAPHER / VIDEOGRAPHER', 'One Personal Photo / Videographer during the entire trip, including a filming permit.', 19, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(110, 345, 4, 'MEMBER LUGGAGE', 'Up to 200 Kg of member’s luggage during the trek carried by porters and helicopter.', 20, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(111, 345, 4, 'MEMBER PERSONAL EQUIPMENT', 'Clothing, Packing Items, Bags, Personal Medical kits, and all kinds of Personal Trekking / Climbing Gear.', 21, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(112, 345, 4, 'FOOD AND LODGING', '3 meals (no limit) a day (breakfast, lunch, and dinner; including tea and coffee) along with accessible accommodation at Hotel/Lodge during the trek and at the Basecamp. Hygienic and fresh green vegetables, fresh meat, fruits, soft drinks, and juice will be served regularly during the entire expedition using helicopter flights. Well-managed base camp set up for members & Staff.', 22, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(113, 345, 4, 'DRINKING', 'Hot water, tea, coffee, beer, wine, etc. during the trek and the Expedition is of no limit.', 23, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(114, 345, 4, 'PORTER', 'Porters per member up to the basecamp and from the basecamp (both ways).', 24, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(115, 345, 4, 'BASE CAMP STAFF', 'Experienced and well-trained Base Camp Cook & kitchen Helpers as required.', 25, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(116, 345, 4, 'PRIVATE COOK', 'A private cook is provided during the entire expedition, preparing a variety of European, Continental, Asian, and Chinese meals for the members during both the trek and expedition.', 26, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(117, 345, 4, 'STAFF SALARY AND ALLOWANCE', 'All Nepalese staff & porter’s daily wages, salary, equipment, food & clothing.', 27, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(118, 345, 4, 'BASE CAMP TENT', 'Each member will have an individual box tent in Base Camp.', 28, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(119, 345, 4, 'BASE CAMP EQUIPMENT', 'Single Box Tent, foam mattresses and pillow per member, 1 Dinning Tent, 1 Kitchen Tent, 1 Communication tent, 1 Toilet & 1 Shower Tent, 1 Staffs Tent, 1 Tent for Nepalese base camp staff, Store tent, Tables & chairs & all necessary cooking gears.', 29, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(120, 345, 4, 'WHITE DOME TENT', 'One White Big Dome luxury tent, for dining, coffee station, and relaxation.', 30, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
(121, 345, 4, 'COFFEE/SPARKLING WATER/ALL BEVERAGE', 'All kinds of hot and cold beverages will be served during the trek and at the base camp.', 31, 1, '2022-03-27 09:35:38', '2023-02-28 07:57:25'),
