(19, 'Everest Weather Report', 'Everest-Weather-Report', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Going on an expedition is a risky job as you are dealing with high altitude, rough terrain, and most importantly the weather as your physical capabilities will be tested at every altitude you gain. Every climber should know the status of the weather situation in these mountain conditions. There will be frequent changes in the weather at this altitude that can make an impact on your expedition.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We cannot predict or change the weather conditions while in the mountains but with the information on the weather forecast, we can plan our climb. For a more precise weather forecast on the mountains follow the links provided below:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.mountain-forecast.com/peaks/Mount-Everest/forecasts/8850\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.mountain-forecast.com/peaks/Mount-Everest/forecasts/8850</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.meteoexploration.com/en/forecasts/Everest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.meteoexploration.com/en/forecasts/Everest/</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.meteoblue.com/en/weather/week/mount-everest_nepal_1283416\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.meteoblue.com/en/weather/week/mount-everest_nepal_1283416</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://everest-pwa.nationalgeographic.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://everest-pwa.nationalgeographic.org/</a></p>', 345, '2022-03-27 04:10:41', '2022-09-13 06:17:56'),
