(12, '2', 'Cancellation', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">We understand that </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">circumstances</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\"> can change, and it may become necessary to cancel a booked trip. To effectively manage operational costs associated with personnel and resources allocated to each trip, we have implemented the following cancellation policy. Please carefully review the terms outlined below:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">Cancellation Fees</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15pt 0in; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif;\">2(a) Cancellation 45 Days Before Departure:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> If you decide to cancel your trip 45 days or more before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The company will charge a cancellation fee of 30% of the total trip amount.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The remaining amount will be refunded to you after deducting the processing charge of Nepal Rastra Bank.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Alternatively, if you prefer, the refundable amount can be retained by the company as a charge for your future trip to China.</span></u></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15pt 0in; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif;\">2(b) Cancellation 25 Days Before Departure:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> If you decide to cancel your trip between 25 days and 44 days before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The company will charge a cancellation fee ranging from 40% to 50% of the total trip amount.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The remaining amount will be refunded to you as outlined in the terms of clause 2(a).</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15pt 0in; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif;\">2(c) Cancellation 1 Week Before Departure:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> If you decide to cancel your trip between 24 Days and the last week before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The company will charge a cancellation fee ranging from 60% to 70% of the total trip amount.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">The remaining amount will be refunded to you as outlined in the terms of clause 2(a).</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15pt 0in; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif;\">2(d) No Refund Once the Trip Begins:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\"> Once your trip has commenced (Started), there will be no refund available for any unused services or portions of the trip. You will be responsible for paying the full amount of the trip in this consequence.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">Please Note:</span></strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\"> Cancellation fees are based on the total trip cost and reflect the expenses incurred in preparing for your journey. We strongly recommend purchasing comprehensive travel insurance to protect against unforeseen circumstances that may necessitate trip cancellation.</span></em></p>', '2', '2021-03-13 19:58:11', '2024-08-16 07:40:34'),
(13, '2', 'Late Booking', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #0d0d0d; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 242; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">Late booking can be done as early as 40 days before the departure from your country. But it is to be noted that it will involve additional cost.</span></p>', '3', '2021-03-13 19:58:11', '2024-08-16 07:40:34'),
