(59, '2', 'Early Trip Termination', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">Clients who choose to prematurely end their trip due to personal emergencies or unforeseen circumstances will incur additional charges. These fees account for the logistical complexities involved in adjusting arrangements, including the return of porters and management of other operational requirements from the base camp. This process typically requires one to three days.</span></p>', '12', '2022-02-20 08:53:42', '2024-08-16 07:40:34'),
(60, '2', 'Flight Cancelations (International/ Domestic)', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">In any flight cancellations, financial compensation will not be provided unless the cancellation is directly caused by the company’s actions. However, </span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #0d0d0d; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 242;\">it is within the duty of the company</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\"> to assist our clients by arranging hotel accommodations, subject to applicable charges.</span></p>', '13', '2022-02-20 08:53:42', '2024-08-16 07:40:34'),
(61, '2', 'Overnight Stay & Food', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">In the event of an overnight stay necessitated by client circumstances, flight cancellations (domestic or international), or any other issues, clients will be responsible for associated accommodation and meal expenses. However, if the overnight stay is caused due to the company’s reason, the company will cover the costs of accommodations.</span></p>', '14', '2022-02-20 08:53:42', '2024-08-16 07:40:34'),
