(95, '30', 'Cancellation', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We understand that circumstances can change, and it may become necessary to cancel a booked trip. To effectively manage operational costs associated with personnel and resources allocated to each trip, we have implemented the following cancellation policy. Please carefully review the terms outlined below:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Cancellation Fees</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2(a) Cancellation 45 Days Before Departure:</strong> If you decide to cancel your trip 45 days or more before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>The company will charge a cancellation fee of 30% of the total trip amount.</li>\r\n<li>The remaining amount will be refunded to you after deducting the processing charge of Nepal Rastra Bank.</li>\r\n<li><u>Alternatively, if you prefer, the refundable amount can be retained by the company as a charge for your future trip to China.</u></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2(b) Cancellation 25 Days Before Departure:</strong> If you decide to cancel your trip between 25 days and 44 days before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>The company will charge a cancellation fee ranging from 40% to 50% of the total trip amount.</li>\r\n<li>The remaining amount will be refunded to you as outlined in the terms of clause 2(a).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2(c) Cancellation 1 Week Before Departure:</strong> If you decide to cancel your trip between 24 Days and the last week before the scheduled departure from your country, the following terms will apply:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>The company will charge a cancellation fee ranging from 60% to 70% of the total trip amount.</li>\r\n<li>The remaining amount will be refunded to you as outlined in the terms of clause 2(a).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2(d) No Refund Once the Trip Begins:</strong> Once your trip has commenced (Started), there will be no refund available for any unused services or portions of the trip. You will be responsible for paying the full amount of the trip in this consequence.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Please Note:</strong><em> Cancellation fees are based on the total trip cost and reflect the expenses incurred in preparing for your journey. We strongly recommend purchasing comprehensive travel insurance to protect against unforeseen circumstances that may necessitate trip cancellation.</em></p>', '2', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(96, '30', 'Late Booking', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Late booking can be done as early as 40 days before the departure from your country. But it is to be noted that it will involve additional cost.</p>', '3', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2023-12-15 05:13:07'),
(97, '30', 'Required Documentation', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients must submit a passport-sized photograph, complete the necessary forms, and provide a certificate verifying the successful summit of a peak exceeding 7,000-meter elevation upon trip confirmation. The company will not be held responsible for any issues arising from the client’s failure to submit the required documentation within the specified timeframe.</p>', '4', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(98, '30', 'Insurance and Travel Risks', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients are required to purchase comprehensive travel insurance before departure, providing coverage for medical expenses, evacuation, and search and rescue missions. Given the inherent risks associated with trekking and expedition activities, particularly in high-altitude environments, we strongly recommend comprehensive insurance coverage for helicopter evacuations, trip cancellations, and personal accidents.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The company will collect client insurance information to facilitate necessary actions in the event of emergencies. In the case of a rescue, the company will coordinate with relevant rescue services and manage related paperwork. However, the company assumes no liability or financial responsibility for any losses or expenses not covered by the client’s insurance policy. Clients are solely responsible for all costs not covered by their insurance provider.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is important to note that air evacuation options may be limited or unavailable in certain regions, such as China. Clients should be prepared for this possibility. While the company will provide support within the constraints of local regulations, the ultimate responsibility for client safety and well-being rests with the individual.</p>', '5', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(99, '30', 'Delay in Entry to China', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Delays in entry to China due to unforeseen circumstances may occur. In the event of such delays preventing clients from entering the country as scheduled, any additional costs incurred due to an extended stay beyond the package duration will be the responsibility of the client.</p>', '6', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(100, '30', 'Visa-Related Issues', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Visa approval is solely the responsibility of the client and is considered a personal matter. While we will assist with visa procedures, we cannot guarantee visa issuance. The Chinese government may deny a visa application based on nationality or other personal reasons. In such cases, Seven Summit Treks Pvt. Ltd. is not liable for visa denial. Refunds for the package will be processed in mutual agreement with the client, subject to applicable charges.</p>', '7', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(101, '30', 'Incomplete Trips', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients will not be entitled to any compensation if they are unable to commence or complete the trek or expedition due to personal reasons, including but not limited to injury or illness. Additionally, in the event of a government-mandated permit revocation due to unforeseen circumstances such as natural disasters, the company will not be liable for any refunds or compensation.</p>', '8', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(102, '30', 'Client Compliance and Authority', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients must agree to adhere to all local laws, regulations, and customs during their trip. The company bears no responsibility for clients engaging in any illegal activities. In the event of a client\'s unlawful conduct, the company reserves the right to contact local authorities. Any legal consequences arising from a client\'s actions are solely the client’s responsibility. The company is under no obligation to provide legal assistance or financial compensation in such circumstances.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The team leader or guide holds ultimate authority during the trek/expedition. These individuals are highly experienced and their decisions prioritize the safety and well-being of all participants. Clients agree to follow their instructions without exception. In the event of disputes or conflicts among clients, the company’s staff will mediate. If necessary, local authorities may be involved to resolve the matter.</p>', '9', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(103, '30', 'Itinerary Modifications and Additional Costs', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seven Summit Treks Pvt. Ltd. offers carefully designed standard packages based on extensive industry experience. We understand, however, that individual preferences may vary. Upon request, we can modify itineraries to accommodate specific client needs, provided that additional time and costs are agreed upon at the time of booking.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:82\">Circumstances beyond our control, such as adverse weather conditions or unforeseen events, may necessitate changes to the itinerary or pricing. In such cases, adjustments will be made in mutual agreement with the client.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-sourcepos=\"9:1-9:179\">Client-induced factors such as damage to company equipment, itinerary delays, requests for additional services beyond the original agreement, etc., are likely to increase the previously decided price.</p>', '10', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(104, '30', 'Early Completion of Schedule', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sometimes schedule may be completed a few days before the designated time, in such cases, no refund will be issued for the unused portion of the itinerary. For example, a 14-days trip concluded in 12 days will not result in a refund for the remaining 2 days.  As outlined in clause 2(d) of these terms, no refunds will be provided once a trip commences.</p>', '11', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(105, '30', 'Early Trip Termination', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients who choose to prematurely end their trip due to personal emergencies or unforeseen circumstances will incur additional charges. These fees account for the logistical complexities involved in adjusting arrangements, including the return of porters and management of other operational requirements from the base camp. This process typically requires one to three days.</p>', '12', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(106, '30', 'Flight Cancelations (International)', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In any flight cancellations, financial compensation will not be provided unless the cancellation is directly caused by the company’s actions. However, it is within the duty of the company to assist our clients by arranging hotel accommodations, subject to applicable charges.</p>', '13', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(107, '30', 'Overnight Stay & Food', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the event of an overnight stay necessitated by client circumstances, flight cancellations (domestic or international), or any other issues, clients will be responsible for associated accommodation and meal expenses. However, if the overnight stay is caused due to the company’s reason, the company will cover the costs of accommodations.</p>', '14', '2023-12-15 05:05:39', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(108, '30', 'Agreement of Accommodations', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trekking and expedition destinations often present challenging conditions far removed from modern conveniences of the 21st century. In some instances, clients may not get exactly what they are looking for, even if they are willing to pay for it. As a hosting company, we try to provide the highest level of service. Unexpected events may occasionally arise where we are unable to meet specific expectations. We appreciate clients\' understanding and flexibility in adapting to such situations. Most importantly, clients must have a clear comprehension of the potential challenges and limitations associated with their chosen itinerary before booking.</p>', '15', '2023-12-15 05:13:07', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(109, '30', 'Meals', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We have carefully selected the best available hotels, tea-houses, lodges and experienced cooks for basecamp and in higher camps. However, the taste may differ from your usual preferences. We prioritize providing the best possible food options, but clients are expected to follow the guide\'s recommendations when selecting menu items.</p>', '16', '2023-12-15 05:13:07', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(110, '30', 'Stuff and Equipment', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If Seven Summit Treks Pvt. Ltd. provides any materials, gear, or equipment, whether owned by the company or not, the client is obligated to return it to the company\'s designated representative upon completion of the trip, expedition, or trek. Any damage incurred to the equipment must be compensated for at a rate determined by the company.</p>', '17', '2023-12-15 05:13:08', '2024-08-08 07:42:16'),
(111, '30', 'Publicity', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seven Summit Treks may request clients’ permission to use photographs and videos captured by clients, free of charge. Any materials provided will be used exclusively for marketing and promotional activities. Client privacy is paramount and will be strictly protected. We appreciate the clients’ cooperation in this matter.</p>', '18', '2023-12-15 05:13:08', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(112, '30', 'Children', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">All children below the age of 16 are required to be accompanied by their legal guardian.</p>', '19', '2024-08-08 07:42:16', '2024-08-08 07:52:58'),
(113, '30', 'Extra Activities', '<p>Clients must inform Seven Summit Treks of any desired extra activities, such as skiing, drone flight, paragliding, or waving large flags, prior to the commencement of the trip. These activities may incur additional fees imposed by the Chinese government. Undertaking such activities without prior notification constitutes a violation of regulations and may result in legal consequences and additional costs, for which the client is solely responsible. If informed beforehand, Seven Summit Treks will assist in obtaining necessary permits and complying with relevant procedures. However, it is important to note that permits for certain activities may not be obtainable. In such cases, the company cannot guarantee a permit.</p>', '20', '2024-08-08 07:42:16', '2024-08-08 07:45:12'),
(114, '30', 'Modifications/ Changes in Itinerary', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients wishing to modify their itinerary must notify Seven Summit Treks via email at least two weeks prior to the departure date. Please refer to clauses 2 and 10 of these terms for our cancellation and modification policies, respectively. If changes necessitate the cancellation of non-refundable items such as government permits, travel tickets, or insurance, the client will be responsible for associated costs. Additionally, clients will be liable for any cancellation fees incurred for airfares purchased on their behalf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> </p>\r\n<p>For any questions or concerns related to these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<p>info@sevensummittreks.com</p>\r\n<p>+977 9801238848</p>', '21', '2024-08-08 07:42:16', '2024-08-13 05:18:58'),
(118, '1', 'Extra Activities', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients must inform Seven Summit Treks of any desired extra activities, such as skiing, drone flight, paragliding, or waving large flags, prior to the commencement of the trip. These activities may incur additional fees imposed by the Government of Nepal. Undertaking such activities without prior notification constitutes a violation of regulations and may result in legal consequences and additional costs, for which the client is solely responsible. If informed beforehand, Seven Summit Treks will assist in obtaining necessary permits and complying with relevant procedures. However, it is important to note that permits for certain activities may not be obtainable. In such cases, the company cannot guarantee permit.</p>', '18', '2024-08-09 09:19:31', '2024-08-09 09:40:25'),
(119, '1', 'Modifications/ Changes in Itinerary', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients wishing to modify their itinerary must notify Seven Summit Treks via email at least two weeks prior to the departure date. Please refer to clauses (2) and (10) of these terms for our cancellation and modification policies, respectively. If changes necessitate the cancellation of non-refundable items such as government permits, travel tickets, or insurance, the client will be responsible for associated costs. Additionally, clients will be liable for any cancellation fees incurred for airfares purchased on their behalf.</p>\r\n<p>For any questions or concerns related to these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<p>info@sevensummittreks.com</p>\r\n<p>+977 9801238848</p>', '19', '2024-08-09 09:19:31', '2024-08-13 05:18:08'),
(120, '2', 'Children', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">All children below the age of 16 are required to be accompanied by their legal guardian.</p>', '19', '2024-08-16 07:40:34', '2024-08-16 07:52:45'),
(121, '2', 'Extra Activities', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clients must inform Seven Summit Treks of any desired extra activities, such as skiing, drone flight, paragliding, or waving large flags, prior to the commencement of the trip. These activities may incur additional fees imposed by the government of Pakistan. Undertaking such activities without prior notification constitutes a violation of regulations and may result in legal consequences and additional costs, for which the client is solely responsible. If informed beforehand, Seven Summit Treks will assist in obtaining necessary permits and complying with relevant procedures. However, it is important to note that permits for certain activities may not be obtainable. In such cases, the company cannot guarantee a permit.</p>', '20', '2024-08-16 07:40:34', '2024-08-16 07:52:45'),
(122, '2', 'Modifications/ Changes in Itinerary', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Clients wishing to modify their itinerary must notify Seven Summit Treks via email at least two weeks prior to the departure date. Please refer to clauses (2) and (10) of these terms for our cancellation and modification policies, respectively. If changes necessitate the cancellation of non-refundable items such as government permits, travel tickets, or insurance, the client will be responsible for associated costs. Additionally, clients will be liable for any cancellation fees incurred for airfares purchased on their behalf.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15.0pt 0in 15.0pt 0in;\">For any questions or concerns related to these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15.0pt 0in 15.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d;\">info@sevensummittreks.com</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 15.0pt 0in 15.0pt 0in;\">+977 9801238848</p>', '21', '2024-08-16 07:40:34', '2024-08-16 07:52:45');
