aration peaks for 8000ers mountains.</p>', 'permit-fees-of-nepal-mountaineering-association-nma-peaks', 5, 0, 0, 3, '31-GmoYZqDLY5N457E0LJJP6pdfjnBjLkmYe1JaUlBg.jpg', 'permit-of-nma-MAxP9FTeXCBHWlai26XkJp0O4aolhoU8P9HDzLjP.jpg', '1644918359971395479', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2022-02-15 09:45:59', '2024-03-17 07:06:16'),
(22, 1, NULL, 'Permit Fees for Trekking in Nepal', 'Permit Fees for Trekking in Nepal', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trekkers are required to have a valid permit for the region they want to trek. These permits may differ from one region to another. Trekkers must have a special permit issued by the Department of Immigration for trekking in restricted areas and other trekking permits for the rest of the regions from authorized associations controlled and supervised by the government.</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trekkers are required to have a valid permit for the region they want to trek. These permits may differ from one region to another. Trekkers must have a special permit issued by the Department of Immigration for trekking in restricted areas and other trekking permits for the rest of the regions from authorized associations controlled and supervised by the government.</p>', 'permit-fees-for-trekking-in-nepal', 5, 0, 0, 4, 'untitled-11-pZEGNT9OqxGAMmtkQP5rpOpgsA8rHO1aDByQvxWr.jpg', 'trekking-permit-dTGRqaKRYA6iZqPAll19Lobvbo16kgRnUIXUD6dk.jpg', '1644918515132392630', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2022-02-15 09:48:35', '2024-03-17 07:18:16'),
(23, 1, NULL, 'COVID-19 Travel Update', 'COVID-19 Travel Update', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The client who intends to take part in our expedition or trekking program in Nepal:</strong> As per the latest decision of the Government of Nepal (Council of Ministers), all passengers traveling to Nepal by air or land route no longer require a fully vaccinated proof of certificate or negative PCR test report for COVID-19.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\">For any further information please feel free to contact us. Thank you for your kind cooperation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\">Regards,&nbsp;<br />Seven Summit Treks&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />Kathmandu, Nepal&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />Contact: +9779801238848</p>', NULL, 'covid19-travel-update', 3, 0, 0, 2, 'untitled-10-PAMlpuBW81k0bDslDJ7tTmObbXaJ2RpLfxipdqOq.jpg', 'covid-19-IYlVhc3yrcTLC5oRzVRCQaEXmxEcJdRVRleVAvN8.jpg', '1645350972105098058', 'Seven Summit Treks; Covid-19 Updates; Travel Updates', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', 'en', '2022-02-20 09:56:12', '2024-08-02 06:22:03'),
