olid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"360\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">After the completion of all rotations and if a member decides not to go for the summit push</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 269.75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"360\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin;\">60-70%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">TIPS:</span></u></strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\"> </span></u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">In mountaineering expeditions, tipping (TIPS) is essential for the income of porters, guides, staff, basecamp workers, and high-altitude workers. Tips for cooks, kitchen assistants, and support staff at base camp are usually pooled and distributed based on service quality during the expedition period and are mostly given at the expedition\'s end to show respect and gratitude for the team\'s hard work and critical support.</span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184; mso-padding-alt: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 269.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: #FBE4D5; mso-background-themecolor: accent2; mso-background-themetint: 51; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"360\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.0pt; font-family: \'Bebas\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Calibri Light\';\">TIPS (MANDATORY AFTER REACHING BC)</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 269.75pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: #FBE4D5; mso-background-themecolor: accent2; mso-background-themetint: 51; padding: 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"360\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.0pt; font-family: \'Bebas\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Calibri Light\'; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">PRICE IN USD</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 1;\">\r\n<td style